IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. OCCURS_SAMPLE.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  TABLE-ITEMS.
    05  ITEM-DETAILS OCCURS 5 TIMES.
        10  ITEM-ID        PIC 9(5).
        10  ITEM-NAME      PIC X(20).
        10  ITEM-PRICE     PIC 9(5)V99.
01  I PIC 9(1).
01  P PIC 9(1).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PROGRAM.
    MOVE 1 TO ITEM-ID(1)
    MOVE 'Apple' TO ITEM-NAME(1)
    MOVE 100 TO ITEM-PRICE(1)

    MOVE 2 TO ITEM-ID(2)
    MOVE 'Banana' TO ITEM-NAME(2)
    MOVE 200 TO ITEM-PRICE(2)

    MOVE 50 TO P

    PERFORM DISPLAY-ITEMS
    STOP RUN.

DISPLAY-ITEMS.
    PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > 5
        DISPLAY ITEM-ID(I) ' ' ITEM-NAME(I) ' ' ITEM-PRICE(I)
    END-PERFORM.
